author: cmpilato
msg: This script now takes an optional REVISION argument to enable one to
build a distribution of an arbitrary revision of Subversion.  Also,
rather than using the revision number of your working copy's README
file to (mis-)name the distribution, use the actual repository
revision number at the time you start the dist-roll.  Warn the user
if his docs/ directory doesn't appear to be sync'ed up with the
version of the source he's tarballing.
